headline: CLH Stock Declines 15% Since Reporting Q3 Earnings Miss: Here's Why
summary: Clean Harbors shares plunge after reporting third-quarter 2025 earnings and revenue misses despite year-over-year rallies and an upbeat 2025 cash flow outlook.
